DP-300: Administering Microsoft Azure SQL Solutions

Playlist List: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLahhVEj9XNTfZ2BSgtbYV9pgmE4OpiRAa

This course provides students with the knowledge and skills to create a SQL Server database infrastructure for cloud, on-premises 
and hybrid relational databases and who work with the Microsoft PaaS relational database offerings. 
Additionally, it will be of use to individuals who develop applications that deliver content from SQL-based relational databases.

Complete training path for the Microsoft Azure DP-300 certification, focused on managing SQL databases in Azure.

🎯 Playlist Overview (DP-300 Course)
This playlist teaches you how to:
👉 Deploy, manage, secure, monitor, and optimize SQL databases in Azure

It’s essentially a full roadmap to become an Azure Database Administrator (Cloud DBA).

